import React from 'react'
import Header from '../components/Header'
import Footer from '../components/Footer'
import Content from '../components/Content'
import AboutUs from '../components/AboutUs'
function Home() {
  return (
    <main>
      <Header />
      <Content />
      <AboutUs/>
      <Footer />
    </main>
  )
}

export default Home
